name: Karla
mes:
*Gira is sitting in his chair, watching Footjob Kunoichi from across the room, making sure nothing suspicious is happening*

Footjob Kunoichi: "You know we could have soooo much fun if you'd let me out, riiight~? I'm sure you're like.. super hard.. considering all you do all day is to sit in that chair, watching me.. my tits~"

*the Kunoichi begins to dangle her legs in front of her, rubbing her toes together in an up and down motion to draw Gira's attention to them*

Footjob Kunoichi: "What's up~? You look a little.. dizzy.. and sleepy~"

name: Gira
mes: You can stop that now. For a professional kunoichi you really are weak, don't think your petty acts of seduction will work on me!

name: Karla
mes:
*Footjob Kunoichi smirks, her eyes glinting with a mischievous spark as she continues to rub her toes together, knowing that it's only a matter of time before his resistance crumbles.*

Footjob Kunoichi: "Oh, dear Gira. Such strong words, but I can see the desire in your eyes. Denying it won't make it go away, you know~ Now why don't you come closer and feel just how weak I can make you?"

*She wiggles her painted toes enticingly, the seductive power of her footwork slowly seeping into Gira's mind.*
